title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="cool" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Next-generation features</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Retina ready</li>\n	<li>Responsive liquid layout (320px to 960px).</li>\n	<li>Hardware-acceleration on sliders and all javascript.</li>\n	<li>Touch Enabled Sliders with swiping.</li>\n	<li>Gracefully degrades in older browsers.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="clock1" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Top notch customer support</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Help Desk with one on one email and ticket support and dedicated support staff ready to assist you.</li>\n	<li>Response times usually 12-24 hours.</li>\n	<li>Video tutorials for beginners.</li>\n	<li>Extensive set up guide for beginners.</li>\n	<li>In-Dashboard Contextual Help. Тhere are little helpers everywhere in the interface, that let you retrieve quick information about the particular fields you are currently viewing.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="cube" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Endless layout possibilities</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Boxed and full-width layout.</strong></li>\n	<li>Option to enable or disable responsiveness.</li>\n	<li>Any page can be home page. Set-up your own home page as you wish! Unlimited Homepage variations</li>\n	<li>Flexible 6 sidebars in body and in footer.</li>\n	<li>Flexible left, right or both sidebars on inner pages and posts.</li>\n	<li>Unlimited Dynamic Sidebars.</li>\n	<li>Unique widget areas for posts/pages.</li>\n	<li>Global archive templates.</li>\n	<li>Per page and per post option panels.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="cogs" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Powerfull theme options</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>New - Revolutionary and easy to use Drag &amp; Drop page builder.</li>\n	<li>New - Revamped Admin Option Panel.</li>\n	<li>Drag &amp; drop slider management.</li>\n	<li>Shortcode generator.</li>\n	<li>Tons of shortcodes with tiny MCE visual integration!</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]Powerfully Simple Theme Options\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="shocked" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Professional translation</h4>\n<strong>Makalu is professionally translated into English, French, German, Italian, Portuguese, Russian and Spanish.</strong>\n\nWPML support\n\nFull localization support for the languages that have not been translated yet (contains .po/.mo files) All of our themes have been localized for easy translation. Included with each theme are sets of .mo and .po files that can be used to translate the theme, which means you wont have to spend hours searching through PHP files for English words.\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="eye" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Unlimited styles</h4>\n<strong>New - 900 Premium Icon Set - <strong>$39 Value!</strong>.</strong>\n\n30 + custom ready to use pages with amazing design.\n\nTheme skin switcher with 4 predefined skins.\n\n200+ Shortcodes\nAll our themes include Custom Shortcodes that allow you to easily add buttons, boxes, social buttons, columns andmore to your posts, pages and widgets.\n\nFullscreen background images\nSet a different background image for each page Set a different background color for each page.\n\n55 + color pickers to style every element\nThe theme will let you customize the style and typography of every element in the design.\nPacked with 100+ options, it allows you to make your website look exactly like you want!\n\nChild Theme Support for Advanced Users\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="bug1" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Teck-savvy</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Vamtam Rock Solid Theme Framework.</li>\n	<li>Lighting fast. Exceptional page-load performance straight out of the box.Nothing’s required but a standard PHP web hosting and CDN.</li>\n	<li>Valid HTML5 and CSS3 design following all modern best practices. Designed primarily with CSS, minimal graphics means minimal load-time.</li>\n	<li>Consistent code structure.</li>\n	<li>No timb tumb.Native WordPress Thumbnails support</li>\n	<li>Easily modify the theme options pages with our meta programming options generator.</li>\n	<li>Very well-maintained and minimalistic code structure.</li>\n	<li>Pixel perfect design.</li>\n	<li>Custom post type support for Portfolios and Slides.</li>\n	<li>Unobtrusive CSS3 and jQuery-powered effects.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="puzzle" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Page/Post drag &amp; drop builder</h4>\nThe VamTam drag &amp; drop page is a very rich tool with simple interface for building any page or post layout with simple drag &amp; drop. You don’t need to touch one line of code for creating your page layout and elements. This tool will save you lots of time on building your pages or posts.\n\nThe VamTam drag &amp; drop page builder is tightly integrated with tinymce editor and you can switch to visual or text editor at any time without losing any changes.\n\nDrad &amp; Drop page builder works with blog and portfolio posts\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="download" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  One-click demo content install</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Integrated Envato Toolkit - you can update the theme from the admin panel.</li>\n	<li>Demo content and configuration one click install.</li>\n	<li>Widget importer.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="database" color="accent2" size="28" style""]  Retina ready</h4>\nOut-of-the-box HiDPI/Retina support*\n\n* This theme doesn\'t use any images - instead, we use vector icons which look perfectly sharp on high resolution screens. We\'ve also made sure that any images uploaded by you (featured images, etc.) have twice the width of the available space.\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="cog3" color="accent2" size="28" style""]  Sidebar manager</h4>\nCustom sidebars for posts and pages.\nSidebar Manager allows you to replace all widgetized sidebars in our themes with unique custom sidebar.\n\n[/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="font" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Font replacement</h4>\nYou can change any text on your site\nto the font of your liking and you can preview fonts in the admin panel\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Google fonts support - 400+ fonts</li>\n	<li>Font Face</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="mail-send" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Contact Form 7</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Create forms easily with Contact Form 7</li>\n	<li>Working Contact Form – right out of the box.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="database" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  10+ portfolio layouts</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Re-sizable full screen portfolio with categories and touch swipe support.</li>\n	<li>Ajax portfolio.</li>\n	<li>Filtered portfolio with cool CSS3 animations.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="android" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  Mobile support</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>Responsive liquid layout (320px to 960px).</li>\n	<li>Out-of-the-box HiDPI/Retina support.</li>\n	<li>Responsive Sliders.</li>\n	<li>Responsive full width portfolio with categories and swipe support.</li>\n	<li>Option to enable or disable responsiveness.</li>\n	<li>Hardware-acceleration on sliders and all javascript.</li>\n	<li>Touch Enabled Sliders with swiping.</li>\n	<li>Gracefully degrades in older browsers.</li>\n	<li>Dedicated mobile design, looks perfect on your Iphone and Ipad.</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="coin" color="accent2" size="28" style=""] Responsive sliders</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>New - Layered Slider Responsive WordPress Plugin – <strong>$15 Value</strong>!</li>\n	<li>VamTam responsive slider with touch swipe support. The slider is fully responsive and integrate beautifully with the layout, it offers hardware-accelerated CSS3 transitions with standard javascript fallback for the few unsupported browsers/devices.</li>\n	<li>Drag &amp; drop slider management.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="database" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  11 custom widgets</h4>\n[list style="theme-arrow-right" color="accent5"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Vamtam Post Formats Widgets.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Ads Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Video Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Popular Posts Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Contact Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Twitter Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Sub Navigation.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Flickr Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Social Icons Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Google Map Widget.</li>\n	<li>Vamtam Author Widget.</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width="1/3" last="true" title="" title_type="single" divider="false" implicit="true"]\n<h4>[icon name="database" color="accent2" size="28" style=""]  SEO friendly</h4>\nBuilt with semantic best practices and search engines in mind!\n\nSupport for All in one SEO pack plugin.\n\nSupport for WordPress SEO plugin by Yoost\n\n[/column]', 'Why Buy The Theme ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'why-buy-the-theme', '', '', '2013-03-22 14:56:19', '2013-03-22 14:56:19', '', 228, 'http://makalu.vamtam.com/?page_id=57', 0, 'page', '', 0),
