	(248, 1, '2013-03-22 18:14:18', '2013-03-22 18:14:18', '[blockquote cite="Richard Pearson"]Vamtam have gone way beyond the normal levels of support and are quick to address any questions\nI have had in a patient and very friendly manner.\nI am not a Wordpress expert and after just 1 hour of editing and uploading my site\nis already looking something like I hoped it would.\n<p lang="bg">I wish these top notch guys all the best with everything they produce and hope that\nthat gets the spoils they deserve from Progressio and any future themes they produce.</p>\n[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Jody LaRue"]Thanks for your help. I’ll be keeping an eye out for future themes by you.[/blockquote]\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Csomortáni Botond"]\n\nThanks for you great support!  Keep up the good job!\n\n[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Amy Hannay"]Thanks so much for the support and again… loving the theme![/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Kristy Crabtree"]You guys ROCK ! Thank you so much.[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Dave Meaden"]Thanks Mario, your support is by far the best I\'ve experienced, and I look forward to future themes from your company.[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Rob"]Our company has been buying on Envato marketplaces for a while now.\nWe buy many things everyday. Vamtam’s level of support is second to none.\nWe have never been so happy to work with a developer from Envato before.\nThere product is perfect and the best we have seen.\nWe highly recommend Vamtam.[/blockquote]\n\n \n[blockquote cite="Denis St-Amour"]You guys really know customer service.\nThanks for making my life easy!! And a huge thanks to Mario![/blockquote]\n \n[blockquote cite="Amber"]Just a quick thank you for all the help and support.\n\nI have been a member for 5 years and purchased 100’s of themes, I highly recommend this theme to anyone considering it.\n\nAmazing versatility and options… sooo many tasty options, this template can easily be anything you want it to be,\nwrap this up in a coating of outstanding support and you have yourself a yummy package worth a lot more than the asking price.\n\nThank you for a great product!\n\nAmber\n[/blockquote]\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Karen"]As a web business owner, I have reviewed many websites in the past and tried many to..\nI would like to say a big thank you for the Studium theme.\n\nThe featured rich options and features are second to none, and having the layout possibilities are tremendous.\n\nThank you so much for making this theme available, and for replying quickly to questions.\n\nNow, can’t wait to get things set up\n\nBest regards.\n\nKaren[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="calvaryconcepts.com"]I have wor ked with dozens of theme authors.\nI want to express my sincerest gratitude in your tireless efforts to resolve and quickly resolve all questions and perceived issues.\nMost issues were resolved immediately in a response.\nYour ticketing system at the Vamtam support is great and I would like to see you build that knowledge base up with the comments on Themeforest.\n\nYou modified a custom plugin to be compatible with your theme which was necessary as a key feature on the website.\nMy experience has been great and will gladly support your future themes.\n\nbest support of all my experience with themes at themeforest. bar none the best. Thanks Nikolay[/blockquote]\n\n \n\n[blockquote cite="Eddy"]OK so I have had some time to get to grips with this theme with the help from the fantastic support at support.vamtam.com\nInitially I was quite daunted by the amount of customisation one can do with this theme, especially the slider concepts\nwhich make total sense now!\nI think this is one of the most beautiful themes in themeforest and on top of that the best one I have ever used to get\nmy site looking how I want it to look.\nWell done guys for a great theme.[/blockquote]\n\n \n[blockquote cite="Richard James Molloy"]Hi Nikolay,\n\nI’ll be more than happy to rate your theme 5 stars, I can honestly say it is by far the best theme I have worked with.\n\nMany thanks.[/blockquote]\n', 'Hall of Fame', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hall-of-fame', '', '', '2013-03-22 18:14:18', '2013-03-22 18:14:18', '', 228, 'http://makalu.vamtam.com/?page_id=248', 0, 'page', '', 0),
